---
By: Dalai Lama
Source:
  URL: https://twitter.com/DalaiLama/status/977115277367349250
  Locus:
    Date: 23 Mar 2018
---
World peace can only be based on inner peace. If we ask what destroys
our inner peace, it's not weapons and external threats, but our own inner
flaws like anger. This is one of the reasons why love and compassion are
important, because they strengthen us. This is a source of hope.
